<div><head>北征記</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.2">彭城，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.3">城北六里有山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.4">臨泗水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.5">有宋桓魋石槨，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.6">有奇石隱起，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.7">龜龍麟鳳之形。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.8">柏谷，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.9">谷邑也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.10">漢武帝微行至此，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.11">為老父所窘者也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.12">谷中無迴車地，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.13">夾以高原，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.14">柏林蔭藹，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.15">窮日幽暗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-1a.16">殆弗覩陽景。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-2a.2">華山對河東首陽山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-2a.3">黃河流於二山之間，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-2a.4">聞本一山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-2a.5">巨靈所開，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-2a.6">今睹手跡於華山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-2a.7">腳跡在首陽山下。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-2a.8">山陽縣城北二十里，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-2a.9">魏中散大夫嵇康園宅，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-2a.10">今悉為田墟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-2a.11">而父老猶謂嵇公竹林地，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1722_CHANT_001-2a.12">以時有遺竹也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
